{"type": "article", "id": 2198, "title": "磁力花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:05:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222251RG7tT6xqOoV4SPyE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">挪威设计师 Hallgeir Homstvedt 日前为丹麦设计品牌 </span><a href=\"http://www.muuto.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Muuto </a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">打造了一款名为 “ Balance ”的花瓶，由一块托盘与一组造型各异的花瓶组合而成，使花瓶与托盘连结在一起的是磁铁，以保证花瓶直立在托盘之上。Hallgeir Homstvedt 希望这样的设计能够激励使用者的好奇心与创造力，让使用者亲自动手来创造花瓶的整体造型，不管有没有鲜花，它都可以是一款个性的装饰物。Balance 将于本月 5 日在巴黎举行的 </span><a href=\"http://www.maison-objet.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">Maison &amp; Objet 贸易展览会</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">上展出。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134858cJ4sWDyjnmp3HZYB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134858ze4HZNFjYKqtG17I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261348595wUyvc7WoztBmLeM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}